snippet.title: Zafe's Adventures - SAGE '24 Trailer
snippet.description:
Here we go with official trailer for my own small game project that I made.
Coming to SAGE 2024 this time. Full release coming when it's done or someday in 2024. Sorry about some blurry quality.

Play the free demo here:
https://gamejolt.com/games/zafeadventures/838455

Music: Slight Change by Macro Brake
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=idZ-V3kZGp4

TuanBaoDoratom / TuanBao Games
2024
